I"4<h1 id="docker-配置文件权限不足警告的消除">Docker 配置文件权限不足警告的消除</h1>

<p>Docker CLI 命令出现权限不足的 warning 时，</p>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span>docker <span class="nb">help
</span>WARNING: Error loading config file: ~/.docker/config.json: open ~/.docker/config.json: permission denied
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>一般来说，原因是 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.docker</code> 目录不属于当前用户。</p>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nv">$ </span><span class="nb">chown</span> <span class="nv">$USER</span> ~/.docker/config.json
</code></pre></div></div>

:ET